            <h5 class="center">Educational Gamification</h5>

            <p class="light">The best way to get students to remember something is to have fun doing it. Using DigiQuiz provides a way for students to play some of their favorite games while reviewing material they learned in class. It is easy to create questions and answers, and the responses are recorded and can be reviewed later on, one-on-one. You can even use it to administrate exams!</p>
