            <p class="light">While the idea of playing games in class has been around a while, DigiQuiz uses the technologies your students already have in order to engage the whole class at once. Calling on a student engages one student - calling on all the students at once is possible with DigiQuiz. Every student participates.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col s12 m4">
